divs: Sighting Detailslocation johnsonville tenn. looked at the johnsonville bridge watching cars go over it. out of no were i saw round red lights in the sky over the tree tops go up in the sky and disaper. i thought at first it was flairs. but was not. i was on a towboat at the time when i saw it. i was shocked at first. i would see two or three in the sky at a time on and off go high then be gone. this lasted about five mins.i lost sight behind the island at the t.v.a. plant.
